00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:50.560
loss. Frank has suffered the same fate as&nbsp;
his friend. He reunites with his family,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:50.560 --> 00:12:54.480
eating at the same table, sharing laughs&nbsp;
and stories. As they say their goodbyes,&nbsp;&nbsp;

